/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/
build/

### VS Code ###
.vscode/

### .DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# 支付证书相关移除
paicoding-web/src/main/resources/cert

